::Shadow Wing::

Pulling out more wire and replacing it with useable wires.  She 
checked a few lines and replaced more of them.  She put in a few 
power surge protectors and disconnected a few old power packs that 
were melted together.  She crawled out from under the console and 
looked for her screwdriver.  She was covered with soot and ash and 
grease.  She found it and crawled back in under the console.  She 
fixed a few more circuits and crawled back out.  She went back to the 
enginering room and found a spare mother board and a few CPU's that 
she could connect to fix Teletran with.  She took it all back up to 
the computer room and started working again.
